 <body ><br><h1 class="pHead1" >
assert_win_unchange
</h1>    
<a name="wp3719613"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that the value of a specified expression does not change in a specified window between a start event and an end event.  </p>    <div align="left" class="tbl">
<table border="0">
  <caption></caption>
  <tr align="left" valign="top">    <td><a name="wp3719628"> </a><div class="pCellBodyLeft" >
