ASSERT_WIN_UNCHANGE
</div>    
</td>
    <td><a name="wp3720505"> </a><div class="pCellBodyLeft" >
The <em class="cEmphasis">test_expr</em> expression changed value during an open event window.
</div>    
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>
	
